    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Teachers are well educated and we'll experienced with good practical knowledge",
          "name": "Aditi sharma",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Staffs are too educated always help us and conduct symposium",
          "name": "Nandhakumar S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college environment is good and also they allow sport's",
          "name": "Nandhakumar S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen is good. it provides food apart from snacks.Both veg & non veg is given.",
          "name": "Manthra",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The environment is very good to learn. It is full of trees, peacocks, so natural.",
          "name": "Manthra",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are lots of clubs in this college, which encourages other talents among students. There are club for tamil, English, photography, tedx, ieee, aerospace etc..",
          "name": "Rohith",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placements coming to my college are top notch, the average package in my batch is 8lpa. I have attended more than 20 companies (both it and non it) and i got placed in a well reputed company.",
          "name": "Rohith",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Teaching , learning was super.They also communicate with students easily.And it could be understandable.There is lot of communication between students and facilities.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Campus was very nice to survive.Lot of social interaction are there,They running clubs like intersect with other.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure was good.Staffs are so communicated.According to me canteen have to develop it will be better.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "There is no campus life here for me it doesn't feels like college it kind of school",
          "name": "Faiz Lone",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure is very poor since it's old college",
          "name": "Faiz Lone",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "They don't have too much infrastructure ,like the Hostel are not too much good.",
          "name": "Aditi sharma",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel foods are not good and also management is not good",
          "name": "Nandhakumar S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Lab equipment are not good and buildings are too old",
          "name": "Nandhakumar S",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Each block is far distanced.We have to walk a lot from department to class and vice versa.",
          "name": "Manthra",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel food will be less than average, students have to tolerate, there are lot of stalls available outside.",
          "name": "Rohith",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Less lab equipments only having, improvement of lab facilities need.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some departments had few placement only.Much more companies could come it will be useful for students.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Actually the building were old.Because thay celebrated platinum jubilee.",
          "name": "Anisha M",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ]
    },
